                     <interp inst="t18281023-109-person637" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a cabinet-maker, and live in Cox Head-court. I was present on the <rs id="t18281023-109-cd641" type="crimeDate">23d of July</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18281023-109-off638 t18281023-109-cd641"></join> last, at the marriage of the prisoner to 
